description: Package Description
ZNxtApp.Core.Module.App is ZNxtApp core app nuget package. This module contains base APIs for the ZNxtApp

$ dotnet new -i Paulovich.Caju::0.3.2
$ dotnet new caju

Will be created a .NET Solution with a layered backend (Domain - Application - Infrastructure - UI) with the Clean Architecture Style. You can choose Hexagon or Event Sourcing styles.
summary:
Try the following commands:

      $ dotnet new caju --use-cases basic --name "MyBasicProject"
      $ dotnet new caju --architecture-style hexagonal --name "MyHexagonalProject"
